Description: Home use only, never gigged. Neck fits tight, no cracks at neck joint. This is the 920D custom shop 2013 Fender Telecaster with Seymour Duncan humbuckers, Babicz full contact bridge, Planet Waves locking tuners, maple fret board and neck, alder body with string thru design, and gloss black finish. She had the TC active EMG pickups, but IMO they were NOT all that (they stunk up the joint: flat out), so after a few months I got rid of all that 'battery jazz' and had a pair of Seymour Duncans (a JB and a '59) professionally installed, along with top of the line pots and caps. I also put on a blacked out pick guard and black pick guard screws: she is now ALL that AND a big ol' black bag of chips. Believe it. She stays in tune for days and sustains for hours. If you never tried the Babicz full contact bridge & saddles, it's quite simply the best electric guitar bridge invention in the last 50 years. Since these pics were taken I have reinstalled the original black Fender logo neck plate and the black strap buttons. She's just how she oughta be, and ready to make some ear drums bleed. Her name is Ouija. There are a few small nicks and pick marks on the pick guard, plus 2 small indents on the face, and one serious OOPS near the jack where the strap failed and it fell on my fuzz pedal (see pics). There is NO belt buckle rash (see pics), so at least I got that right. The head stock is mint, front & back. I will ship her in a crappy Fender plastic molded case, just so nothing happens in transit (all 3 latches work, as does the handle and hinges). A great song writer, she gave me and my crappy li'l punk rock band (Drunks with Guns) quite a few decent toe tappers the last few years. And what good is a guitar if there aren't any songs left in her? The neck is flawless, no nicks at all, front or back, so where it counts, this guitar is in excellent shape. I am the original purchaser, it's just time to thin the herd. Buyer pays actual shipping via UPS ground in a 48x18x8 box weighing less than 15 lbs.
Title: Fender Telecaster electric guitar 920D Custom Shop BABICZ SEYMOUR DUNCAN HSC MIM
